added.title: El Padre
added.description: Los niños intentan ayudar a Papá a hacerse amigo de Frankie.
added.originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

added.title: La Incomodidad
added.description: Gumball y Chico Salchicha descubren por qué se sienten tan incómodos el uno con el otro.
added.originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

added.title: La Fe
added.description: Alan perdió su fe en la humanidad y puso el mundo blanco y negro. Gumball tiene que superar el odio que siente hacia Alan para recuperar el color a través del canto.
added.originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

added.title: Billy and Mandy Moon the Moon
added.description: When cheese-obsessed alien invaders from the Moon abduct Billy, Mandy, and Grim, it's up to our heroes to save the world's dairy supply with magic, kung-fu, and a good nose-picking.
added.originalseriesname: The Grim Adventures of Billy and Mandy

added.title: El Caballero de la Tele
added.description: Batman y el comisionado Gordon salen a presenciar varios sucesos que ocurren cerca de Jump City.

added.title: Caballero TV 2
added.description: Batman y el Comisionado Gordon hacen una pijamada para mirar sus programas de televisión favoritos.

added.title: Caballero Televisivo 3
added.description: Batman está más interesado en ver televisión que en participar de su fiesta de cumpleaños.

added.title: Aye, Aye, Eyes/Dee Dee and the Man
added.description: Aye, Aye, Eyes: When Dexter returns a little girl's stuffed bunny to her, she falls in love with him. With the help of Dee Dee, Dexter is eventually able to divert the girl's affections toward another little boy./Dee Dee and the Man: Fed up with Dee Dee's constant destruction of his lab, Dexter fires her. Finding a replacement, however, is more difficult than he thought. It turns out she provides the perfect amount of distraction.

added.title: The Garden/Sheboodles
added.description: The Garden: Impressed with Truffles' gardening skills, Chowder takes her on as his new master. Saddened over the loss of his apprentice, Mung tries to win him back./Sheboodles: A lonely Miss Endive decides to cook herself a man-dish for a date. But when she rushes the dish, it goes horribly wrong.

added.title: Rent-A-Ed/Shoo Ed
added.description: Rent-A-Ed: Eddy and Edd form a repair company using Ed as their multi-purpose tool. The Eds go into kids' homes to repair broken things. Unfortunately, Ed breaks everything he touches./Shoo Ed: Jonny 2x4 irritates Kevin by hanging around him all the time. When Kevin asks the Eds to get rid of him, Eddy realizes they could run a lucrative Jonny pest control business.

added.title: La material de brillo importa
added.description: Cuando Unikitty se entera de que el viejo y aburrido Richard nunca produjo materia de brillo feliz, iprepara una fórmula con la Dra. Fox que lo sobrecargará de emociones! iAhora, Richard produce tanta materia de brillo que amenaza con destruir el reino! ¿Podrá Unikitty ayudar a Richard a encontrar el equilibrio emocional antes de que todo desaparezca?

added.title: Courage Meets Big Foot/Hothead
added.description: Courage Meets Bigfoot: A hungry Bigfoot turns up at the farm. Courage is terrified at first but befriends the gentle monster and must save him from Eustace and an angry mob./Hothead: Eustace goes to a hair institute that promises hair growth dragging Courage along with him. The consequences that follow are hair-raising.

added.title: Bosque de accion
added.description: Hawkodile es el héroe de acción más rudo de la zona, hasta que su viejo rival llega para vengarse de él. Derrotado y necesitado de ayuda, Hawkodile debe entrenar a Unikitty y a los otros para que se conviertan en compañeros superfuertes y musculosos. Y solo hay un lugar donde surgen guerreros imparables, el Bosque de Acción.

added.title: Gatita kaiju
added.description: Cuando un monstruo gigante ataca el Unireino, la banda se defiende con la impresionante nueva arma secreta de la Dra. Fox: iun mega robot gigantesco! Pero después de contener la amenaza, Unikitty no quiere dejar de usar el increíble robot, así que encuentra excusas para usarlo para todo, sin importar qué tan inútil sea. Pero, ¿y si ellos resultan ser la mayor amenaza para el reino?

added.title: Skooled/Snarked!
added.description: Skooled: Flapjack thinks he's a dummy so K'nuckles takes him to school where they both have an adventure in learning./Snarked!: Fearing Bubbie has been abducted, Flapjack and K'nuckles go undercover aboard a mysterious foreign ship.

added.title: Operation: C.A.B.L.E.-T.V./Operation: C.A.M.P.
added.description: Operation: C.A.B.L.E.-T.V.: A kid's cable network executive believes the Kids Next Door would be perfect for their own show on his kid-centric network, but when the exec's nefarious motives are revealed, the Kids Next Door decide not to follow the program./Operation: C.A.M.P.: Numbuh One suspects the neighborhood kids shipped off to summer camp are being brainwashed by the camp's evil commander. His daring rescue mission hits a snag, however, when Numbuh Two and Numbuh Three suddenly have new priorities.

added.title: Who Let the Dogs In?
added.description: When Eduardo finds a puppy in the house, he must keep it a secret due to Mr. Herriman's strict rule of no dogs in the house.

added.title: Secrets
added.description: Grandpa Max's mysterious past comes to light when Vilgax shows up on earth in search of the Omnitrix. And the family must work together to defeat him.

added.title: Space Cow/The Legend of Sailcat/Happy Baboon Holidays
added.description: Space Cow: Cow and Chicken both win a contest that allows them to spend a day in the career of their choice.  Cow chooses to be an astronaut, and gets sent up on the space shuttle.  Chicken says he wants to go where the real money is - marketing, and becomes a bag boy at the local supermarket. The Legend of Sailcat: Flem's Dad takes Chicken, Flem and Earl on a camping trip in the woods, where they're having fun telling scary stories around the campfire.  When Cow crashes their campout (literally), the boys become upset.  So Flem's Dad distracts them by singing the scariest, creepiest story of all - The Legend of Sailcat - a musical epic about a cat who gets flattened by an 18 wheeler and goes on to become a hero of the highways. Happy Baboon Holidays:  (Weasel)  Weasel charms Baboon's family at Christmas time.  Hurt and outraged, Baboon sets out to leave booby traps for Santa on Weasel's roof.

added.title: The Lady and the Queen/The AB's Silver Screen Debut
added.description: The Lady and the Queen: China Riot finds a new Bakugan: Barbetra. But this buzzy new Bakugan is a bit timid on the battleground. Riot takes her on as her new project to turn her into the battle queen she knows she can be./The AB's Silver Screen Debut: Lord Brakken and Duran have teamed up and are now the Bakugan film business. They look to the Awesome Brawlers for their expertise in both Bakugan culture and film making to get their movie made!

added.title: Haunted House/Two of a Kind
added.description: Haunted House: Rumor has it that there's a haunted building in Los Volmos, and the Awesome Brawlers are on the case! Who doesn't like a good ghost hunt, plus capturing a ghost on camera should make Awesome Brawlers' next video a huge success!/Two of a Kind: Veronica Venegas is doing a special report on the Awesome brawlers own: Lightening! The special report takes a back seat when Lightening is challenged to a brawl. Lightening uses this brawl the perfect opportunity to rollout his new Bakugan partner: Tretorous.

added.title: Bakugan Wynton/The Boy from Brazil
added.description: Bakugan Wynton: Wynton has a new device that tracks down Bakugan! Right out of the gate the device works and, Wynton meets: Batrix. Like his name, Batrix is a little batty, and these two are certainly in for a "batty" first adventure./The Boy from Brazil: The Awesome Brawlers are off to a soccer match! In the process of doing so Shun discovers a new Bakugan friend, the boisterous Ramparian, and a new foe in Brazilian soccer star: Pepe.

added.title: The Bakugan Battle League/The Ancient Elder
added.description: The Bakugan Battle League: Benton Dusk is in the process of renovating a state of the art Bakugan Brawling stadium. When it comes to brawling, who better to test out the new arena than the Awesome Brawlers!/The Ancient Elder: Dan finds a new baku-bud in Gillitar. Well "bud" may be too strong a word, Dan and gang quickly learn that Gillator has a few "quirks" that keep him from fitting in with the rest of the Awesome Brawler's Bakugan.

added.title: Nice to Meet You, Bakugan!/Magnus
added.description: Nice to Meet You, Bakugan!: After the Tiko incident, Bakugan brawling with a device has become extremely restricted. But there will always be people using devices to control Bakugan for evil. Magnus has taken it upon himself to step in and stop these villains and their wrongdoing./Magnus: After the Tiko incident, Bakugan brawling with a device has become extremely restricted. But there will always be people using devices to control Bakugan for evil. Magnus has taken it upon himself to step in and stop these villains and their wrongdoing.

added.title: The Alliance Part 2
added.description: Autobots and Decepticons unite, launching a massive assault on the Quintesson ship.

added.title: The Scientist Part 2
added.description: While Hot Rod and Soundwave battle the indestructible Scientist, Perceptor and the rest of the team attempt a mass breakout from the Loop.

added.title: The Alliance Part 1
added.description: Freed from the Loop, Optimus and Megatron still have trouble reconciling so it's up to Hot Rod and Soundwave to unite the divided Cybertronians against the Quintesson invaders.

added.title: The Scientist Part 1
added.description: In order to heal Soundwave's glitch and find out how to free the Autobots and Decepticons from the Loop, the team hunt down a mysterious Quintesson called The Scientist.

added.title: La Jaula
added.description: Los niños convencen al Sr. Corneille de que se suba a un cuadrilátero y le organizan una pelea contra un temible luchador ruso.
added.originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

added.title: Los Jovenes Titanes vrum: primera parte
added.description: En este episodio de "Fuerza Turbo Titanes", los Titanes obtienen la habilidad de convertirse en autos.

added.title: Los Jovenes Titanes vrum: segunda parte
added.description: En la emocionante conclusión de "Fuerza Turbo Titanes", los Titanes deben aprender a trabajar juntos para detener al Doctor Militar.

added.title: El Grupo
added.description: Gumball y Darwin intentan unirse a la pandilla de los más malos de la ciudad.
added.originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

added.title: Duelo en la Piscina
added.description: Unikitty y la pandilla se están divirtiendo mucho en la piscina pública, hasta que intentan que Perricornio nade en la parte profunda con ellos. A Perricornio le da muchísimo miedo ir a lo más profundo. Ahora Unikitty y la banda deben ayudarlo a superar su miedo para que se divierta al máximo en la piscina. Mientras tanto, Master Frown y Brock están tramando un plan para arruinar la diversión de todos: quitar el tapón de la piscina. Ahora Perricornio debe dominar su miedo para detener a los que quieren estropear la diversión.

added.title: Letras Desastrosas
added.description: La pandilla está planeando una sorpresa para Puppycorn, así que deletrean las cosas cuando hablan para que él no se entere. Desesperado por saber lo que dicen, Puppycorn encuentra un libro mágico que cree que lo ayudará a aprender a deletrear, ipero sin saberlo, el libro le enseña a lanzar hechizos! ¿Se dará cuenta Puppycorn de que el conocimiento es poder, y de que algunos secretos se guardan por una razón?

added.title: Kitty y Halcon: Protectores de la Ley
added.description: Cuando el juguete favorito de Perricornio desaparece, Unikitty y Halcondrilo se unen para localizar al ladrón, ial estilo socios policías! Pero cuando las cosas se ponen difíciles y el caso no se resuelve, ya no es solo su sociedad la que está en juego, sino también su amistad.

added.title: Momento Perfecto
added.description: Cuando Halcondrilo admite su amor por la Dra. Fox, Unikitty y sus amigos se convierten en sus gurús del amor para ayudarlo a confesar sus sentimientos por ella. Por desgracia, los grandes planes de Unikitty para el momento perfecto del amor lo complican todo.

added.title: Amigo roca
added.description: Unikitty descubre que el único otro amigo de Puppycorn es una roca vieja y aburrida. Incentivado a ""hacer más amigos"", Puppycorn no puede encontrar a alguien con quien sienta afinidad, hasta que sigue el consejo de Unikitty y decide literalmente hacer un nuevo amigo con las mejores partes de sus amigos. Esto no irá bien.

added.title: Caos en la cocina
added.description: Después de lesionarse en su lugar de trabajo, Richard no puede hacer sus tareas de criado. Unikitty y los demás se encargan de una simple tarea: limpiar la cocina. Esta actividad increíblemente aburrida es un desafío para nuestros héroes, que buscan todas las formas posibles de no hacerla. ¿Serán capaces de alcanzar esta meta y traer de regreso a Richard?

added.title: El Ultimo robo
added.description: K.O. decide ayudar a Ginger a redescrubrir sus tiempos de gloria.
added.originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

added.title: TKO
added.description: Parte 1: En busca de poder, K.O. acepta la ayuda de una figura misteriosa./ Parte 2: Nuestros héroes se alían para salvar la Plaza de una nueva amenaza.
added.originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

added.title: El poder es tuyo
added.description: Un héroe especial ayuda a Plaza Lakewood Turbo a salvar el planeta.
added.originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

added.title: Plazaolimpiadas
added.description: K.O. participa de la competencia anual de Plaza Turbo: los Plazalímpicos.
added.originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

added.title: Dia de padres
added.description: It's Parents' Day at Lakewood Plaza Turbo!
added.originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

added.title: El primer episodio de esqueleto y brandon
added.description: Un Esqueleto Mágico Real descubre una nueva oportunidad laboral.
added.originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol
